{"tid":1547874,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"9·6 旺角E1出口𠝹刀阿叔，香港人醒撚未啊","createTime":"2019-09-06T22:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T01:12:00.000Z","uid":121408,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a2469644702d63e52950bacfe96b6c6a3cff78b3","tid":1547874,"uid":121408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T22:34:14.000Z","msg":"(借ac)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家次撚次都有廢老意圖傷害手足啊！點解到今日仲有咁多人叫唔好打！仲要有人上前關心佢遞埋紙巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家抗爭緊啊，唔係建設緊關愛共享社會！<br />\n<br />\n呢啲人唔好以為自己大愛，其實只係助紂為虐，害死其他手足。就係班廢老每次都無後果，咪斬人斬上癮，出完𠝹刀又有另一單菜刀喇。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得應該出新職業：劊子手，見親呢啲廢老就一齊拉去暗角好似七警咁行私刑，唔郁手嘅人就幫手落雨。"},{"pid":"cc70d75408802bd4069135fe2184da5e1c0f1614","tid":1547874,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T22:34:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一句講晒，睇哩個post</span></span><br />\n[置頂/請廣傳/多圖] 907 遊客LOOK 暢遊大嶼山指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547426</a>"},{"pid":"47bea9efcea582406dc3478bb8e8fe972d8c1823","tid":1547874,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T22:45:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">提防散水消息 前車之鑑話俾我地聽機場係安全到不得了</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ahsi61O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fahsi61O.jpg&h=c4cbdea2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UYMWTGP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUYMWTGP.jpg&h=d86ae932&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dTCZRtv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdTCZRtv.jpg&h=ae815516&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lm8aX8v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLm8aX8v.jpg&h=a1475d47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://n